    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸在情感艺术隐藏物品游戏的温馨世界中。</h2>《Love is...》是一款由全球知名艺术家“Puuung”创作的手绘插画情感艺术隐藏物品游戏。在寻找隐藏物品时，体验水彩扩散和填充画作的美丽。伴随着温馨的故事，发现新的隐藏物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/37ed6c8c957a30e26f324757b0583322.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/37ed6c8c957a30e26f324757b0583322.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/37ed6c8c957a30e26f324757b0583322.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找隐藏物品，完全上色并完成美丽的画作。</h2>当你找到隐藏物品时，颜色会扩散，美丽地填充画作。完成超过280幅充满情感的手绘水彩插画。《Love is...》独特的着色引擎为您带来情感而强烈的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/3e628ed67042c2b80659be2438a0aa77.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/3e628ed67042c2b80659be2438a0aa77.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/3e628ed67042c2b80659be2438a0aa77.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸在温暖可爱的故事中。</h2>享受温馨的动画，有时宁静，有时幽默的爱情故事。为您准备了超过一小时的高质量故事动画<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/95c51ddeb512a1791e49aeb908624ce7.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/95c51ddeb512a1791e49aeb908624ce7.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/95c51ddeb512a1791e49aeb908624ce7.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保留美丽的壁纸。</h2>每通过《Love is...》中的一个章节，您将获得美丽的壁纸。永远在您的电脑上保存34张令人惊叹的高质量壁纸。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/4388da83d29f82d08ecb7bbcb5ecf9e2.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/4388da83d29f82d08ecb7bbcb5ecf9e2.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/4388da83d29f82d08ecb7bbcb5ecf9e2.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >享受《love Is...》甜美的原声音乐。</h2>享受由钢琴和木吉他演奏的甜美旋律的原声音乐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/d6986cfb6583c5d836e7dd4af681f054.poster.avif?t=1724734627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/d6986cfb6583c5d836e7dd4af681f054.webm?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034130/extras/d6986cfb6583c5d836e7dd4af681f054.mp4?t=1724734627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
